    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    London drug dealer jailed for longer
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Amir Mohamed must now serve an immediate term of imprisonment following an intervention by the Solicitor General, Rt Hon Michael Ellis QC MP. </p>

  </div>
</div>

